Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.88,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便能化為一抹微笑
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.88,0:01:54.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}或許那是悄悄埋下的願望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}讓奇蹟綻放
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.93,0:02:04.65,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}將那最最重要的寶物找到
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.65,0:02:10.94,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便是我們此行的目標
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.94,0:02:17.67,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.15,0:02:26.21,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}也要用希望編織當下
