Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:31.37,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}幸福  寂寞  擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:40.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}都是人生的必由之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:44.75,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一小匙的閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.88,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便能化為一抹微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:54.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}或許那是悄悄埋下的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}讓奇蹟綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:04.65,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}將那最最重要的寶物找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:10.94,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便是我們此行的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:17.67,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:26.21,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}也要用希望編織當下
